CHANGES
=======

2.1.0
-----

* Add SUSHY\_EMULATOR\_VIRTUAL\_MEDIA\_IP\_FAMILY environment variable support
* Validate JSON content type before parsing manager PATCH requests
* Drop test logic for Python < 3.8
